WEBVTT

00:06:28.600 --> 00:06:31.736
that they might give you
over that period of time.

00:06:31.760 --> 00:06:36.216
There is some sort of magic that happens,
I think, between seven and ten days

00:06:36.240 --> 00:06:38.856
when really the honeymoon's over

00:06:38.880 --> 00:06:40.896
and people are really themselves

00:06:40.920 --> 00:06:46.136
and you see people for both
who they are in their great goodness

00:06:46.160 --> 00:06:48.936
and also the challenges that they bring.

00:06:48.960 --> 00:06:53.016
AG: I often see people try to build trust
by meeting once a month for lunch.

00:06:53.040 --> 00:06:56.936
The hope is that once you know
each other well, you'll start opening up.

00:06:56.960 --> 00:06:59.976
But I bet you've had experiences
where that never happens.

00:07:00.000 --> 00:07:02.056
The relationship just
doesn't move forward.